graph TD
    Start([Start: Video Stream Received]) --> CaptureFrame[Capture Video Frame]
    CaptureFrame --> Preprocess[Preprocess Frame<br/>Resize & Normalize]
    Preprocess --> RunDetection[Run Deep Learning Model<br/>YOLOv8/YOLOv9]
    RunDetection --> CheckDetection{Activity<br/>Detected?}
    
    CheckDetection -->|No| CaptureFrame
    CheckDetection -->|Yes| CheckConfidence{Confidence<br/>> Threshold?}
    
    CheckConfidence -->|No| LogLowConf[Log Low Confidence Detection]
    LogLowConf --> CaptureFrame
    
    CheckConfidence -->|Yes| AudioAvailable{Audio<br/>Available?}
    
    AudioAvailable -->|Yes| ProcessAudio[Process Audio Stream]
    ProcessAudio --> AudioDetection[Run Audio Event Detection]
    AudioDetection --> FuseData[Fuse Audio-Visual Data]
    FuseData --> DetermineSeverity
    
    AudioAvailable -->|No| DetermineSeverity[Determine Alert Severity<br/>LOW/MEDIUM/HIGH]
    
    DetermineSeverity --> ExtractClip[Extract Video Clip<br/>10s before, 15s after]
    ExtractClip --> AnnotateClip[Add Annotations<br/>Bounding Boxes & Labels]
    AnnotateClip --> SaveEvidence[Save Evidence to Storage]
    
    SaveEvidence --> CheckSeverity{Alert<br/>Severity?}
    
    CheckSeverity -->|LOW| DashboardAlert[Show in Dashboard Only]
    CheckSeverity -->|MEDIUM| EmailAlert[Send Email Notification]
    CheckSeverity -->|HIGH| MultiAlert[Send WhatsApp + Email]
    
    DashboardAlert --> LogEvent[Log Event to JSON]
    EmailAlert --> LogEvent
    MultiAlert --> LogEvent
    
    LogEvent --> UpdateDashboard[Update Real-time Dashboard]
    UpdateDashboard --> CaptureFrame
    
    style Start fill:#90EE90
    style CheckDetection fill:#FFE4B5
    style CheckConfidence fill:#FFE4B5
    style AudioAvailable fill:#FFE4B5
    style CheckSeverity fill:#FFE4B5
    style MultiAlert fill:#FF6B6B
    style EmailAlert fill:#FFA500
    style DashboardAlert fill:#4169E1